'''南渡'''（{{lang-my|ၼမ်ႉတူႈ}}），是[[缅甸|缅甸]][[掸邦|掸邦]]北部的一个[[镇|镇]]，以其[[包德温|包德温]]和南渡银矿著名。坐落于[[南渡河|南渡河]]，通过{{tsl|en|Burma Mines Railway|缅甸矿业铁路}}与[[腊戍|腊戍]]附近的缅甸米轨铁路相连。<ref name=ICFTU>{{Cite web|url=http://www.hartford-hwp.com/archives/54/266.html|title=ICFTU sends radio message to striking workers at Namtu silver mine|date=11 February 1998|publisher=Hartford Web Publishing|accessdate=2009-02-06|archive-date=2017-04-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170428113342/http://www.hartford-hwp.com/archives/54/266.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://farrail.de/pages/trip-reports-engl/burma-namtu-2006-02.html|first=James|last=Waite|title=The Burma Mines Railway, Namtu|publisher=FarRail Tours|accessdate=2009-02-06|archive-date=2020-08-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200804223325/https://farrail.de/pages/trip-reports-engl/burma-namtu-2006-02.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>1945年日本投降后，当地[[缅甸华人|华侨]]曾修建了两座烈士纪念碑以纪念[[中国远征军|中国远征军]]，今已不复存在。<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.mhwmm.com/Ch/NewsView.asp?ID=1196 |title = 南渡的远征军烈士纪念碑 |author = 朱雪雪 |date = 2012-06-23 |publisher = 缅华网 |language = 中文 |accessdate = 2015-02-14 |quote =  |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150214173904/http://www.mhwmm.com/Ch/NewsView.asp?ID=1196 |archive-date = 2015-02-14 |dead-url = yes }}</ref>

==历史==
南渡包德温（Bawdwin）矿产在[[二战|二战]]前是世界最大的[[铅|铅]]矿产地，也是世界最大的[[银|银]]矿产地之一。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.scarecrowpress.com/Chapters/Index.shtml?SKU=0810854767&Site=scarecrowpress&Title=Historical%20Dictionary%20of%20Burma%20(Myanmar)&FileType=PDF |title=Historical Dictionary of Burma (Myanmar) |publisher=The Scarecrow Press, Inc. |accessdate=2009-02-07 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110727084909/http://www.scarecrowpress.com/Chapters/Index.shtml?SKU=0810854767&Site=scarecrowpress&Title=Historical%20Dictionary%20of%20Burma%20%28Myanmar%29&FileType=PDF |archivedate=2011-07-27 }}</ref>在英国殖民者到来之前（1880年代），南渡的矿产由东本（Tawngpeng）的[[诏法|诏法]]把控，由来自中国云南的中国劳工开展采矿工作。当矿脉到达地下水位之时矿山被废弃了。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.rockmekong.org/pubs/lab-pubs/Paris%20Palaung%20paper.pdf|first=Anchalee|last=Singhanetra-Renard|title=The Palaung of Shan State|publisher=rockmekong.org|date=September 2004|accessdate=2009-02-07|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120305044246/http://www.rockmekong.org/pubs/lab-pubs/Paris%20Palaung%20paper.pdf|archivedate=2012-03-05}}</ref>这些矿山在20世纪初叶开始被英国人重新开发。<ref>{{Cite book|url=http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=qf3XSIJqSZkC&pg=PA173&lpg=PA173&dq=namtu&source=web&ots=cMsEA25rV6&sig=6j5bd5phWy5TtIkEyJKqhtKHkBo&hl=en&ei=IvGNSY_lJpiL-gbJ8eWJCw&sa=X&oi=book_result&resnum=3&ct=result#PPA174,M1|first=Paul H|last=Kratoska|title=South East Asia, Colonial History|publisher=Taylor & Francis, 2001|accessdate=2009-02-07|isbn=978-0-415-21542-8|archive-date=2015-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150215001824/http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=qf3XSIJqSZkC&pg=PA173&lpg=PA173&dq=namtu&source=web&ots=cMsEA25rV6&sig=6j5bd5phWy5TtIkEyJKqhtKHkBo&hl=en&ei=IvGNSY_lJpiL-gbJ8eWJCw&sa=X&oi=book_result&resnum=3&ct=result#PPA174,M1|dead-url=no}}</ref>1906年3月，组建了英资的“缅甸矿业铁路与熔炼有限公司”（The Burma Mines, Railway and Smelting Co Ltd），1907年开始建设铁路，1908年修到了距包德温5km的虎营矿区（Tiger Camp mining area）。1914年与缅甸的{{tsl|en|Northern Shan State Railway|北禅邦铁路}}在Nam-yau站接轨。{{tsl|en|Burma Mines Railway|缅甸矿业铁路}}轨距为2英尺(610 mm)，长80km。

==现状==
现在的南渡矿产处于国家控制之下，由缅甸矿业部门管理。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://mm.mofcom.gov.cn/column/print.shtml?/sqfb/200608/20060802865071|title=Quotations|publisher=Ministry of Mines|accessdate=2009-02-07|archive-date=2011-07-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110707040755/http://mm.mofcom.gov.cn/column/print.shtml?%2Fsqfb%2F200608%2F20060802865071|dead-url=no}}</ref>

铅、[[锌|锌]]和[[镍|镍]]也由矿山产出。锌主要出口到日本，其它矿物在销往国外之前被送到南渡[[冶炼|冶炼]]。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://digicoll.library.wisc.edu/cgi-bin/EcoNatRes/EcoNatRes-idx?type=turn&entity=EcoNatRes.MinYB1974v3.p0220&isize=text|last=Adams|first=Timothy|title=Bureau of Mines / Minerals yearbook area reports: international 1974|publisher=[[University_of_Wisconsin|University of Wisconsin]] Digital Collections|accessdate=2009-02-07|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303204603/http://digicoll.library.wisc.edu/cgi-bin/EcoNatRes/EcoNatRes-idx?type=turn&entity=EcoNatRes.MinYB1974v3.p0220&isize=text|dead-url=no}}</ref>

1998年2月，3,000名工人举行了大罢工，要求提供给他们更好的工作环境和提高井下旷工的工资。<ref name=ICFTU/><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.earthwins.com/ewd/ewd021198a.html|title=Hot Spots|publisher=EarthWINS Daily|date=11 Feb 1998|accessdate=2009-02-07|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070624190529/http://www.earthwins.com/ewd/ewd021198a.html|archivedate=2007-06-24}}</ref>

一家中国的公司于2002年赢得了在南渡建立锌氧化物工厂的合同，这个工厂年加工50,000吨锌渣，生产的氧化锌出口到云南。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://dir.groups.yahoo.com/group/BurmaCourier/message/65|title=Chinese Company Building Zinc Oxide Plant at Namtu|publisher=Burma Courier No. 302|date=January 5, 2002|accessdate=2009-02-07|archive-date=2012-07-07|archive-url=https://archive.today/20120707220504/http://dir.groups.yahoo.com/group/BurmaCourier/message/65|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

==政治==
[[掸邦军|掸邦军]]（SSA-North）第三旅一直活跃在[[孟密|孟密]]、[[皎脉|皎脉]]、[[昔卜|昔卜]]、南渡和[[腊戍|腊戍]]。它在1989年已与[[国家和平与发展委员会|缅甸军政府]]（恢委会）签署停火协议，其活动受到严格限制。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.shanland.org/politics/2005/Ceasefire-group-gets-marching-orders/|title=Ceasefire group gets marching orders|date=2005-08-30|publisher=[[Shan_Herald_News_Agency|S.H.A.N.]]|accessdate=2009-02-04|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090210234607/http://www.shanland.org/politics/2005/Ceasefire-group-gets-marching-orders/|archivedate=2009-02-10}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.shanland.org/politics/1999/truce_brings_only_grief.htm/|title=Truce Brings Only Grief, Says Ceasefire Leader|publisher=S.H.A.N.|date=2005-05-23|accessdate=2009-02-04|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090210233203/http://www.shanland.org/politics/1999/truce_brings_only_grief.htm/|archivedate=2009-02-10}}</ref>巴朗国家解放组织（Palaung State Liberation Organization）也活跃于该地区。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.shanland.org/drugs/2000/palaungs_declare_war_on_drugs.htm/|title=Palaungs Declare War on Drugs|date=2005-06-04|publisher=S.H.A.N.|accessdate=2009-02-07|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090211054454/http://www.shanland.org/drugs/2000/palaungs_declare_war_on_drugs.htm/|archivedate=2009-02-11}}</ref>

